headline.print_headline: Tesco, Waitrose to Launch 'Click and Collect' With London Underground
headline.main: Tesco, Waitrose to Launch 'Click and Collect' With London Underground

lead_paragraph: Supermarket chains Tesco and Waitrose are to begin "click and collect" services across the London Underground network after signing a deal with the city's transport authority.
